      <title>金丝雀码头正在商谈再融资高达 6.03 亿英镑的债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/canary-wharf-in-talks-to-refinance-up-to-603-million-in-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金丝雀码头集团正在与贷方进行谈判，以重新融资高达 6.03 亿英镑（7.93 亿美元）的垃圾债券，并提供其购物中心资产作为债务的抵押品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/canary-wharf-in-talks-to-refinance-up-to-603-million-in-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 15:39:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国税务海关总署在新规出台前解除个人储蓄账户零碎股份禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/hmrc-ends-ban-on-fractional-shares-in-isas-ahead-of-new-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府预计将于今年晚些时候修改规则，英国税务机关已停止执行禁止个人免税储蓄账户持有少于一股股票的规定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/hmrc-ends-ban-on-fractional-shares-in-isas-ahead-of-new-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 14:39:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰希望更改最小货币单位的“俄罗斯”名称</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/ukraine-wants-to-change-russian-name-of-smallest-currency-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰央行正寻求将该国最小面额货币“科比”更名为“沙阿”，并放弃使用“科比”这一与俄罗斯“戈比”过于相似的术语。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/ukraine-wants-to-change-russian-name-of-smallest-currency-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 14:29:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙将于 9 月 4 日宣布新任央行行长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/spain-to-announce-new-central-bank-governor-sept-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙定于周三宣布其新任央行行长，这将结束有关谁将填补近三个月来空缺的长期猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/spain-to-announce-new-central-bank-governor-sept-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 13:59:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利政府接近外汇债务限额，发行武士债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/hungary-offers-samurai-bonds-as-government-nears-fx-debt-limit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利自 2022 年以来首次发行以日元计价的债券，这将使该国政府更接近对该国外汇计价债务设定的限额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/hungary-offers-samurai-bonds-as-government-nears-fx-debt-limit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 13:44:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国 Rightmove 引起默多克 REA 的收购兴趣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/rea-weighs-bid-for-5-8-billion-uk-property-business-rightmove</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国市场份额最大的房地产门户网站 Rightmove Plc 吸引了澳大利亚房地产上市提供商 REA Group Ltd. 的收购兴趣，推动这家在伦敦上市的股票上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/rea-weighs-bid-for-5-8-billion-uk-property-business-rightmove</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 00:44:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价波动，市场关注 OPEC+ 产量和中国需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商权衡 OPEC+ 下个月的增产计划、中国的经济逆风以及利比亚的减产，油价在小幅上涨和下跌之间波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 23:19:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党声称英镑面临威胁，投资者持怀疑态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/uk-risked-run-on-pound-if-fuel-subsidy-had-stayed-labour-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党声称，如果财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 没有取消养老金领取者的燃料补贴，英国可能面临金融动荡。这一说法受到市场参与者的质疑，其中一人称工党的说法“完全是一派胡言”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/uk-risked-run-on-pound-if-fuel-subsidy-had-stayed-labour-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市徘徊，交易员为 9 月波动做好准备：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/asia-eyes-cautious-open-after-china-factory-data-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，全球股市徘徊在历史高位附近，投资者准备迎接通常被认为是股市最具挑战性的月份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/asia-eyes-cautious-open-after-china-factory-data-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 22:31:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁巴比斯可能是捷克紧缩政策的最大赢家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/czechs-propose-another-budget-deficit-cut-for-election-year-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克共和国的中右翼政府将在下一轮预算中加大紧缩措施，此举可能加速民粹主义亿万富翁安德烈·巴比什明年重新执政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/czechs-propose-another-budget-deficit-cut-for-election-year-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 00:13:03 GMT</pubDate>
